{"tid":2312894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（大韓帝國）朝鮮王室後裔出手 千萬美元買下加州2.4萬坪豪宅","createTime":"2020-12-05T10:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T06:08:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c262cc5842ad05daed62ae021e930a7329240db2","tid":2312894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"朝鮮王朝王室後裔安德魯，李（Andrew Lee），在美國加州千橡市豪擲1260萬美元（約新台幣3.5億元），買下占地20英畝（約2萬4483坪）的隱谷（Hidden Valley）社區豪宅。<br />\n<br />\n據《洛杉磯時報》報導，房地產服務公司Multiple listing service的資料顯示，這是千橡市今年交易金額最高的建物，超越2月時以1000萬美元（約新台幣2.8億元）售出的豪華別墅。<br />\n<br />\n安德魯，李購入的房產就像是宮殿一樣，中心坐落著法國風格的豪宅，裡頭有7間臥室、13間盥洗室和富麗堂皇的起居空間，配有訂製家具、吊燈和窗簾，內部設施包括品酒室、電影院和健身房。<br />\n<br />\n據《YTN》報導，安德魯，李出生於美國印第安納州，一手創辦了VPN公司Private Internet Access，他在2013年才知道自己的父親是朝鮮王室後代。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮高宗（朝鮮王朝末期皇帝，由日本扶持脫離清朝，成為君主立憲的大韓帝國開國君主）之孫李錫，於2018年指定Andrew Lee為朝鮮王室「太子」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3372270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3372270&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=ded11766\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3372270&h=b260075c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3372270</a>"},{"pid":"fed34098db08ffab973f8dd85718eb9e3f8a42bb","tid":2312894,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14e52b0acdb0337bedf628d2a9fb7ed0c6a4cb2","tid":2312894,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"仲未俾北韓特工追殺？"},{"pid":"c824a4ec566ff32d5db2e69f53ffc14ee234f49e","tid":2312894,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一手創辦了VPN公司Private Internet Access"},{"pid":"44ed03e170d992b0115e34967a4cbe98c71e2feb","tid":2312894,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/99184/800x_100_w-5e7971628d3bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F99184%2F800x_100_w-5e7971628d3bd.jpg&h=9084f0e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b02a8433c01ca9656b75dee7c98a5d2d254ab430","tid":2312894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}